audio_descriptions.notes:
- Animation
- Ringling College of Art and Design Presents 
- a little boy shuts his bedside lamp off to go to bed
- scene changes from in a room to soaring through clouds 
- The Counting Sheep 
- two sheep are in a meadow, one older sheep and one younger sheep
- a headboard appears from the ground 
- an additional sheep is shown 
- the first bigger sheep hops over the headboard 
- the second much smaller sheep hops over
- a big line of sheep is revealed waiting to hop over the headboard
- the sheeps are numbered up to 100
- the 100th sheep  in line unhappy with the reply
- the sheep cheerfully asks the other sheep is their waiting will be over anytime soon
- sheep exerts frustration and the little sheep shamefully returns to his spot on the line 
- the 100th sheep looks cheerfully at sheep # 98 as is turn was coming up 
- 100th sheep excited to be his turn 
- as the 100th sheep suspends in the air as he hops over the headboard, it disappears, and he falls on the ground on his back
- sheep lays on his back with a look of disappointment and sadness
- the sheep jolts into the air holding a pose mid-air, after performing the jolt looks around the group of sheep for reactions
- sheep still laying on his back 
- looks at his number upside down and reads 001
- the sheep's mood turns around
- sheep closes the rest room door after a sheep entered-- has a cunning smile on his face 
- nails door shut, tapes it over, rips off tapes end 
- uses welding tools to seal edges of restroom
- when done, looks at it proudly and brings out a hair cutter, wonders behind the restroom
- shaves some of his hair off, pieces of fluff are thrown on the ground as it is shaved off
- sheep comes out from behind admiring his haircut
- the haircut reveals that his number is now 1 rather than 100
- sheep inside the stall bangs door, cannot leave the sealed stall
- the sheep now rushes to the front of the line, because he is now #1, 
- the line starts at 100 this time around rather than at 1 
- 99th sheep looking for the 100th sheep
- sheep disappointed at backwards counting, as he will be last to hop once again
- sighs and lowers head to the ground 
- sheep in the stall jolts in the air with the stall
